  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "chapterTitle": "第一回 说楔子敷陈大义 借名流隐括全文",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300138694_5_421-505",
          "range": "421-505",
          "rangeStart": 421,
          "rangeEnd": 505,
          "markText": "人生南北多歧路，将相神仙，也要凡人做。百代兴亡朝复暮，江风吹倒前朝树。功名富贵无凭据，费尽心情，总把流光误。浊酒三杯沉醉去，水流花谢知何处。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1763450362,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-11-18 15:19:22",
          "chapterUid": 5,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300138694&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=421&rangeEnd=505",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/12832e90813ab9cadg014e36?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=421&rangeEnd=505"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300138694_9_827-844",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "827-844",
      "markText": "借此免了秋风之费，真是靠百姓的福。",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300138694&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=827&rangeEnd=844",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/12832e90813ab9cadg014e36?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=827&rangeEnd=844"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300138694_52_5299-5399",
      "chapterUid": 52,
      "range": "5299-5399",
      "markText": "三女儿他而今已是成了仙了，你哭他怎的？他这死的好，只怕我将来不能像他这一个好题目死哩！”［1］因仰天大笑道：“死的好！死的好！”［2］大笑着，走出房门去了。",
      "totalCount": 39,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300138694&chapterUid=52&rangeStart=5299&rangeEnd=5399",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/12832e90813ab9cadg014e36?chapterUid=52&rangeStart=5299&rangeEnd=5399"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300138694_5_12763-12811",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "12763-12811",
      "markText": "这个法却定的不好！将来读书人既有此一条荣身之路，把那文行出处都看得轻了。”［1］〔1〕",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300138694&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=12763&rangeEnd=12811",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/12832e90813ab9cadg014e36?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=12763&rangeEnd=12811"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300138694_6_2955-2970",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2955-2970",
      "markText": "所以要等亲家，所以先发作和尚。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300138694&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2955&rangeEnd=2970",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/12832e90813ab9cadg014e36?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2955&rangeEnd=2970"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300138694_7_2925-2944",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2925-2944",
      "markText": "〔1〕人生世上，势位富厚岂可以忽乎哉？",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300138694&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2925&rangeEnd=2944",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/12832e90813ab9cadg014e36?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2925&rangeEnd=2944"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300138694_8_12798-12834",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "12798-12834",
      "markText": "使拙笔为之，必且曰：看官听说，原来严贡生为人是何等样，文字便索然无味矣。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300138694&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=12798&rangeEnd=12834",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/12832e90813ab9cadg014e36?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=12798&rangeEnd=12834"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300138694_9_5833-5889",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "5833-5889",
      "markText": "何不向你爷说，明日我若死了，就把你扶正做个填房。”［2］赵氏忙叫请爷进来，把奶奶的话说了。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300138694&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=5833&rangeEnd=5889",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/12832e90813ab9cadg014e36?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=5833&rangeEnd=5889"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300138694_9_11806-11829",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "11806-11829",
      "markText": "五个侄子穿梭的过来陪郎中弄药。［3］",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300138694&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=11806&rangeEnd=11829",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/12832e90813ab9cadg014e36?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=11806&rangeEnd=11829"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300138694_5_9018-9030",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "9018-9030",
      "markText": "塘边都栽满了榆树、桑树。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300138694&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9018&rangeEnd=9030",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/12832e90813ab9cadg014e36?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9018&rangeEnd=9030"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300138694_6_7438-7488",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "7438-7488",
      "markText": "那些孩子就像蠢牛一般，一时照顾不到，就溜到外边去打瓦踢球，每日淘气不了。周进只得捺定性子，坐着教导。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300138694&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7438&rangeEnd=7488",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/12832e90813ab9cadg014e36?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7438&rangeEnd=7488"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300138694_7_3042-3082",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "3042-3082",
      "markText": "我在这里面吃苦久了，如今自己当权，须要把卷子都要细细看过，不可听着幕客，屈了真才",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300138694&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3042&rangeEnd=3082",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/12832e90813ab9cadg014e36?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3042&rangeEnd=3082"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300138694_7_12710-12746",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "12710-12746",
      "markText": "“适才看见题名录，贵房师高要县汤公，就是先祖的门生，我和你是亲切的世弟兄",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300138694&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=12710&rangeEnd=12746",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/12832e90813ab9cadg014e36?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=12710&rangeEnd=12746"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300138694_8_11635-11718",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "11635-11718",
      "markText": "大骂一顿“大胆狗奴”，重责三十板，取一面大枷，把那五十斤牛肉都堆在枷上，脸和颈子箍的紧紧的，只剩得两个眼睛，在县前示众。天气又热，枷到第二日，牛肉生蛆，第三日呜呼死了",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300138694&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=11635&rangeEnd=11718",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/12832e90813ab9cadg014e36?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=11635&rangeEnd=11718"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300138694_5_8648-8686",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "8648-8686",
      "markText": "那婆婆道：“其实不在家了，不知在那里。”说毕，关着门进去了。［4］",
      "totalCount": 33,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300138694&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=8648&rangeEnd=8686",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/12832e90813ab9cadg014e36?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=8648&rangeEnd=8686"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300138694_6_1608-1707",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1608-1707",
      "markText": "“俺如今〔1〕倒不如你们务农的快活了！［4］想这新年大节，老爷衙门里，三班六房，那一位不送帖子来，我怎好不去贺节？每日骑着这个驴，上县下乡，跑得昏头晕脑。",
      "totalCount": 33,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300138694&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1608&rangeEnd=1707",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/12832e90813ab9cadg014e36?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1608&rangeEnd=1707"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300138694_5_9503-9527",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "9503-9527",
      "markText": "时知县倚着危素的势要，在这里酷虐小民，无所不为。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300138694&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9503&rangeEnd=9527",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/12832e90813ab9cadg014e36?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9503&rangeEnd=9527"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300138694_6_5243-5303",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "5243-5303",
      "markText": "随即每桌摆上八九个碗，乃是猪头肉、公鸡、鲤鱼、肚、肺、肝、肠之类。叫一声“请”，一齐举箸，却如风卷残云一般，早去了一半。",
